| 1 |  | #P_1st2nd | |- ( ( Rel R /\ A e. R ) -> A = <. ( 1st ` A ) , ( 2nd ` A ) >. ) |

| 5 |  | #P_fvex | |- ( 2nd ` A ) e. _V |
